  "title": "Civil & Structural Engineer (Main Con, Tender)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work with C&amp;S consultants to develop structural schemes and perform engineering analysis to assess stability and load-bearing capacity.</li>\n  <li>Design temporary works for construction activities and ensure compliance with relevant design codes, including Eurocodes.</li>\n  <li>Prepare technical submissions, project quality plans, and submit designs to authorities for approval.</li>\n  <li>Offer technical guidance to team members, participate in project and site meetings, and address technical inquiries while fostering a collaborative environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience as a C&amp;S Engineer in <strong>Construction industry (Main Con).</strong></li>\n  <li>Proven experience in technical tender preparation, including ERSS plans, site utilization planning, and construction methodologies, with knowledge of relevant codes, regulations, and approval processes.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in <strong>Microsoft Project and PowerPoint.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
